text: Welcome to Whispering Meadows. Immaculate new construction home in one of the newest developments in Nooksack. This 4 bed 2.25 bath has it all. Open living with lots of natural light & a cozy fireplace creates a warm & inviting atmosphere. Kitchen features quartz counters, brushed nickel hardware, & SS appliances which offers a modern & stylish space. The main floor master bedroom features vaulted ceilings, huge walk-in closet, & a double vanity in the ensuite bath. Remaining 3 bedrooms upstairs & one of them could be easily used as a bonus room. Ductless mini splits to keep you cool in the summer & warm in the winter. Lets not forget about the deck & private backyard, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities. House is not in the flood zone!
Latitude 49, lot 49

$5, 000 Seller Credit for new Kitchen Counters. Elegant & inviting, updated single-level home nestled in the beautiful Orchard Crest community of Ferndale. This meticulously maintained residence situated on a huge lot offers an inviting open floor plan with tall vaulted ceilings and skylights for lots of natural light. Step onto Brazilian cherry hardwood floors and enjoy marble and travertine tile throughout. A/C, a new roof with a 50-year warranty, ensuring comfort and peace of mind. Solid wood doors, granite vanities, and custom touches add to the home's distinctive appeal. Fully fenced backyard features a large 2-level deck, recently stained, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Appliances are included, making this home move-in ready.

Nature Lovers Paradise! Welcome to this beautiful 3, 100 sqft home in the middle of an outdoor sanctuary with various types of trees, fruit and wildlife. Enter through a tree-lined private drive which opens up to a 15 acre oasis that extends into Lake Fazon. Vaulted ceiling with extensive windows will delight you with the beauty that surrounds w mountain and lake views. This 4 bdrm, 4 barm home has large Douglas Fir posts and beams throughout, a big kitchen w granite countertops w island that opens up to the dining and living rm. The downstairs family rm has a kitchen for a potential mother-in-law suite. Grab your waders and go duck hunt or fish in your back yard! Only 15 minutes to Bellingham, this is a very special one-of-a-kind property.

Large double lot located in the lakeside and golf course community of Sudden Valley. Wonderful south facing property with large evergreens in the neighborhood. The property is a gentle down-sloping lot, making it conducive for a home plan with main level living and a daylight basement below. Plenty of room for a 3-car garage in your house plan as well! Loads of elbow room here! There is potential access below the property coming up from Honeycomb Lane for utilities or a lower driveway to a garage area. Buyer to verify.

Step into this inviting 2-bedroom condo nestled in The Cypress Place Condominiums. Welcomed by a courtyard view, this home boasts a bright and efficient layout designed to enhance everyday living. A well-appointed kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and granite counters, a cozy living room with an electric fireplace, and access to a patio perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, ss well as two designated parking spaces and a storage closet. Enjoy the amenities of Cypress Condominiums including secure entry, elevators, an exercise room, and bike storage - all in a great location close to WWU, trails, shopping, and restaurants.

Situated in the vibrant core of Bellingham is a recently constructed modern duplex, completed in 2022. Within each meticulously crafted unit, discover 2 bedrooms and 1 bath featuring a double vanity. Enjoy personalized comfort with a mini split offering both heating and cooling options. Parking is hassle-free with one covered spot and an additional uncovered space for each unit, complemented by a convenient outside storage unit for your outdoor essentials. The kitchen is a chef's dream, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and cabinets that close with a gentle touch. Enhancing the overall allure, this chic duplex showcases Provenza vinyl floors. Welcome to contemporary living in the heart of Bellingham!

Enjoy stunning bay, island, mountain, and city views from this 2-bedroom, 1.75-bath, 1, 432 sq ft condo. Located in a secure, 55+ community with 15 units, it features an elevator from covered parking to your front door. The kitchen has updated appliances, interior paint, new carpet, and the dining area offers expansive views. The covered deck is perfect for relaxing and entertaining while enjoying spectacular sunsets. The spacious living room includes a gas fireplace, and the primary bedroom has an ensuite bath. Additional features include a stackable washer/dryer, ample storage, and a large shared workshop. Close to WWU, Sehome Arboretum, and Downtown Bellingham.

This home feels better than new! A charming one-level 3 bed, 2 bath corner lot with fresh landscaping and new outdoor living area. This home features stunning hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout interior and exterior. The spacious living room boasts vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace, perfect for relaxing. The modern kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet and an attached bathroom. Located just a short walk from Lynden Middle School and nearby parks, this home is ideal for anyone. Come schedule a private tour today!

Roosevelt neighborhood charmer, walking distance to Trader Joes & Barkley Village, shops, restaurants & parks. Plentiful windows create bright living spaces, several doors lead to fully fenced private back yard with hot tub & garden shed. Entertain + relax in your lush garden with fruit trees & flowering plants. Primary Bedroom on main level, abundant built-in storage, kitchen pantry, mini-split with A/C. Laundry/mud room, spacious 1-car garage + 2 car driveway + plentiful parking on quiet street. New water heater 1-2024, new sewer line 12-2022. Walk score: 71; bike score: 76, near Railroad Trail. Potential ADU opportunity - verify with City. Could also be a great rental property. Buyer to confirm schools.

Rare find, end unit! Tucked in a serene neighborhood off Alabama in the highly desirable Sand Dollar Village Condos! This beautifully cared for one-level home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and an open-concept floor plan! Stylishly updated kitchen with oodles of choice Hickory cabinets, pantry and large eat-in counter. Hickory cabinets in bathrooms as well. Great for entertaining; a vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace adds that homey feel. Retreat to a cozy, covered back patio, enough room to BBQ & host a few guests! Large closets in each bedroom & in the hallway keep you organized. You'll benefit from included yard care; put your feet up! Just minutes to nearby Whatcom Falls Park, downtown Bellingham shops, galleries, WWU & nearby hospital.

This beautiful home is nestled in serene surroundings, this property is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. Imagine immersing yourself in nature's wonderland, steps from your front door. You are only a few minutes from Galbraith Mountain Trails, Lake Padden, and Lake Samish. Within 10 minutes, enjoy Fairhaven, and Downtown Bellingham's vibrant communities with their shops, dining, entertainment. Convivence is the key, with easy access to I-5 for a smooth commute. This thoroughly designed home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and sits on .84-acre lot. Recent upgrades include a new heat pump, Generac generator, exterior and interior paint, added pantry, and extra parking. Don't miss this incredible property combining tranquility and convivence.

Situated in the heart of Edgemoor, this 1988 quality built custom home offers tranquil living in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Bellingham. Meticulously maintained in its original state, this residence radiates a classic charm that never goes out of style. Built on a spacious lot amidst a picturesque backdrop of mature trees and easy-care landscaping. Step through the dining room french doors to a sunny deck overlooking the scenic landscape and fully fenced yard, ideal for outdoor living and entertaining. The main-level primary suite and two upper-level bedrooms, each offer full-size bathrooms and walk-in closets to ensure luxurious comfort. 2 car garage. New roof and furnace. Only two owners since the house was built.

Delightful home in this sought after 55+ community park. Perfectly located within walking distance to Fairhaven's shops and amenities, interurban trail and an abundancy of city parks. This lovely home is at the end of a dead-end street, providing privacy and seclusion. The primary bedroom has a huge en-suite bathroom with double vanity, corner tub and large walk-in shower cubicle. Good size 2nd bedroom and full 2nd bathroom. Kitchen has new quartz countertops and new tiled back-splash, with dining area or recreational area adjacent. Spacious living room and good size office or could be a separate dining room. Recently painted throughout making this home bright and fresh. The rear yard has a lovely decked area to relax. A gem!

Welcome to the architecturally award winning 10th & Taylor Condominiums with Westerly bay views! Experience the ultimate lifestyle with an easy stroll to historic Fairhaven Village, just steps away from Bellingham's iconic waterfront boardwalk and across from the Chrysalis Inn & Spa, featuring one of Bellingham's finest restaurants. The owner, who purchased this condo at the foundation stage of construction, completely redesigned the interior with custom high end cabinetry, appliances, flooring, doors, AC and in floor radiant heat and much more. Enjoy a rare level entry from private alley parking to your front door, and a gated garage for your two cars and storage accessed by an elevator. This is an opportunity to own one of the best!

Light & bright ground-level condo full of updates! This 2 bed, 1.75 bath corner unit faces the serene wetlands so it is more private than the average. Recently remodeled kitchen with new appliances, counters & cabinets. New luxury vinyl plank floors throughout. Primary bedroom with updated en-suite bathroom. Centrally located in Cordata near trails, schools, restaurants and shopping. Central vacuum throughout. Stackable washer & dryer in unit. Handy storage unit off the covered back patio is great for extra space! Move in ready!

Beautiful home with incredible ocean views!!! Single level living and featuring recently refinished Brazilian Cherry Hardwood floors, large windows, and vaulted ceilings. Welcome to your private paradise on of an acre with beautifully mature landscaping and high bank waterfront. Primary suite includes access to the large waterfront decks, a cozy fireplace, large 5 piece bathroom, well designed walk in closet, and an office space. This home was fully redone in 2008 and has had many updates throughout. Large chefs kitchen has plenty of storage and top of the line appliances. Enjoy the large deck with new Trex decking and incredible views over the sound to White Rock and the Canadian Rockies. This is the perfect place to spend your summer!

D-5, 44 foot slip! You can't get much closer to the main dock. Semiahmoo Marina! History, majesty, mystery...what a great place to moor your boat! Semiahmoo's historic water tower stands sentinel. To the East, majestic Mt. Baker...and mystery, why are all those cars cruising Marine Drive in White Rock?! Semiahmoo Marina is only 16 nautical miles from the legendary, mystical San Juan Islands. Canada's Gulf Islands and the Inside Passage are favorite nearby destinations. Golf, tennis and swimming are available for a fee @ Semiahmoo Golf & County Club. Nice facilities, store, laundry and more. 2 hours from Seattle, 36 miles to Vancouver BC. Canada.

Looking for a highly recreational property walking distance to amenities including the golf course, fitness center, outdoor summer pools, lake beaches & more? Then this is it! Spacious 3BR, 2BA condo has been recently updated with all new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout + new paint, trim & lighting. Light & bright updated kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances, quartz tile counters, new hardware & eating bar. Sitting above Lake Louise, you will love the private back deck facing the trees. With a surprising amount of storage, take advantage of the double closets in the primary bedroom, under the stairs storage off the entry and of course the coveted single car attached garage! Enjoy the private condo pool & sport court too!

Nestled off the main road, in the picturesque landscape, this expansive parcel of land offers boundless opportunities for your dream property. This location boasts stunning natural beauty, with panoramic views of the surrounding valley. Spanning 5 acres of lush terrain, this property provides ample space to bring your vision to life. This level lot has a shared well with one other property and an approved 3 bedroom septic permit. Conveniently located between Maple Falls and Sumas you have easy access to the mountain and shopping. Just minutes to Silver Lake where you can enjoy the park, trails, and summer boat rentals. Come check out this beautiful lot and make your dream home a reality!

Nicely maintained condo overlooking a peaceful creek in the heart of Lynden. This 2-bedroom residence has higher-end finishes, seclusion, and convenient proximity to shops and restaurants. Enjoy the open floor plan with cherry hardwood floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, stylish window treatments, and picturesque creek-side views. The primary bedroom is complemented by a spacious bath and a walk-in closet. The massive oversized 2-car garage provides a huge amount of space to complete your projects or provide extra storage.

Spacious one acre lot with perfect flat building site for a great sized shop! Primary bedroom and second upstairs bedroom share a brand new wrap around deck offering stunning views from inside & out. This nearly 2500 soft home offers a versatile layout with a spacious living/hosting room on both the bottom and main floor. Quality craftsmanship is highlighted with a 50 year cedar shake roof and cedar siding. Downstairs bonus room features electric fireplace which could be converted back to gas. All front windows of home have just had glass panels replaced. This home has a 90% high efficiency gas furnace, recently rewired electrical panel, new paint, new carpet, and new kitchen appliances. This full acre lot awaits your new additions!

Charming beach cottage nestled in the Maple Beach community. Featuring 2 beds, 1 bath, and an expansive open-concept layout. Wood fireplace in the heart of the cottage with a stone facade, a large kitchen overlooking the backyard, and a one-car garage. Unwind under the covered patio, or take a leisurely stroll to the beach just moments away, with sandbars for days, and warm bath water in the Summer. Don't miss out on this Point Robert's gem!

Wonderful 3+ bdrm, 3.5 bath, 3052 sq ft Lyndal Cedar home in rural setting, immaculate condition.Easy access to I-5 & Canadian Border. Outdoor living area overlooking 6 manicured acres w/ pond perfect for those private parties and afternoon BBQs. Living room with vaulted ceilings, lots of windows, wood fireplace. Kitchen has granite counters, custom cabinets, skylights, Brazilian hardwood floors. Main bedroom has cozy fireplace, french doors opening to the private hot tub and view of your very own park like setting. Main bath has soaker tub, tiled shower and walk-in closet. 2 other large bedrooms, office, flex room could be separate living quarters. Oversized 2 car garage, 30x36 shop, 300 Ft asphalt drive with covered parking for RV'S

Incredible home on 4.8 acres in secluded area just outside Ferndale proper. This home features a huge deck that surrounds a jetted heated spa and a heated exercise pool. The wrap around porch gives a warm modern farmhouse feel. The long private drive with a circle drive is all blacktopped. Large shop would be great for an auto enthusiast or a hobbyist. The lush grounds has 15 fruit trees, many flower gardens, raised bed gardens, and a 10x12 green house. Delightful kitchen includes a Wolf Gourmet range, custom cabinets, 2 ovens, and a bay window eat in kitchen. All new carpet in 2023. Natural oak floor was refinished, Fresh painted exterior, new roof done in 2023 and 2022 new HP. Guest house has 2 large closets, newer roof and flooring.

Nicely remodeled and fully furnished condo with views of the bay! Located in the sought after Jacobs Landing, this 900 sq/ft end unit with 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, is one of the largest in the complex and a stone's throw from the beach. Spacious great room with soaring ceilings adjoins a large kitchen with updated cabinets, granite countertops and quality appliances. Live the beach life with miles of sandy beaches out your front door, all within walking distance of restaurants, state parks, shopping & more. Come and enjoy all that Jacob's Landing has to offer with an indoor pool, hot tub, tennis courts, racquet ball, and clubhouse. Move-in ready, whether for yourself or to rent! Nightly Airbnb and VRBO approved.

Welcome to 6120 Aquarius Ave, a charming and well maintained 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home in Ferndale. With 968 square feet of comfortable living space, this property offers an inviting open layout on the main floor, seamlessly connecting the kitchen and living room. Upstairs, you'll find all three bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a conveniently located laundry area, providing ease of living. Step outside through the sliding door to a spacious backyard with a gravel patio area, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The property also features a 1-car garage, RV parking, and a new water heater. Just minutes from Skyline Elementary School. Don't miss out on one of the most affordable single family homes in the county!

If you are looking for a fully remodeled home in an established neighborhood, this is it!! This 4 bed/3 bath home has been fully renovated from top to bottom! This home sits on a prime corner lot showcasing its fresh exterior paint job and brand-new fence and rear deck to enjoy the outdoors. As you walk through the front door you will see the new open concept with new flooring throughout, raised ceilings, brand new custom kitchen and bathrooms! Beautiful finish touches with quartz counters, white cabinets, custom tile showers and showcase upgraded lighting throughout! Added bonus of a basement with a full bed/bath/wet bar/and separate entrance for the MIL suite or rental income. This home is truly transformed and is a must see!

Discover this hard-to-find 3 bed/2.5 bath multi-level home in the highly desirable Edgemoor neighborhood. This quality cul de sac location is only blocks from Fairhaven Park & the Bayside Swimming Club. Enjoy the warmth of 2 free-standing gas fireplaces, great natural light, bamboo floors, & Corian countertops. Addt'l features incld attached 2-car garage w/space for workbench, sliding glass door that opens to private patio area perfect for BBQing or relaxing, & a lot that is a gardener's canvas. If that's not enough, go enjoy the views from your spacious perched deck at the rear of the property.Located near schools, parks, Fairhaven, & Chuckanut Dr, this outstanding home offers convenience & beauty of this iconic neighborhood.

Incredible views from Lummi Island and Bellingham Bay to Galbraith Mountain from this beautiful, well designed sun filled home. You will appreciate parking your car, plugging in to your EV charger and stepping into your home office, then into the open concept living area with generous kitchen, ample storage, large dining and living space that leads out to your upper level deck with outstanding views. Down the hall you'll appreciate the primary bedroom with en-suite, powder and utility room. Downstairs you will find 2 bedrooms, a full bath with double vanity, a third large finished room and family room with access to the second porch and fully fenced backyard with a raised garden bed. Stay comfortable year round with one year old AC unit!

Step into history w/ this remodeled 1910 Four Square American Colonial on a fully fenced 5 acres. The charming home features 3 bdrms that live like 4, & 2 luxurious bths. A grand front porch welcomes you. Original staircase, & spacious rooms w/ 10-foot ceilings. Hardwood floors, wood fireplace, designer wall coverings, remodeled kitchen & fresh paint throughout enhances the charm. Studio space downstairs w/ a full bath. Outbuildings include a 3-car garage & a 2-story finished gambrel top shop, potential for an ADU. Surrounded by privacy, youll find a MIL cottage. Start your hobby farm w/ a fenced pasture, hayshed, & lean-to run-in. Close proximity to Birch Bay Beach. This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle to cherish!

Just South of the US/Canadian Border is located an Individually owned 44 Foot Dock / Slip with Condominium Ownership within the Semiahmoo Marina. Well Situated location close to the main gangway on the D Dock - (D6). Water and Power hookups available. Fantastic Marina with Full Laundry Facilities, Restrooms and Dockside Market/Deli. The Marina is adjacent to the popular Semiahmoo Resort, the gated Semiahmoo Neighborhood as well as the Semiahmoo Golf Course. Truly one of the finest neighborhoods in Washington State. Excellent home port for exploring the San Juan Islands, Gulf Islands and Pacific Northwest. Additionally - the boat featured in the photos can be purchased separately.

Geneva Rambler situated on a 12, 000+ SF lot on a serene & luxurious cul-de-sac. This 3BD/2BA home offers many desirable features like finished-in-place oak floors through much of the main living area. The living room is flooded in natural light while enjoying partial lake views & access to a large, sunrise-facing deck. Entertain in the dining room or appoint it as a den, & relish the flexibility of the dine-in kitchen. Spacious Primary Suite w/full bath & walk-in closet. Wide-open 3-car garage offers over 800 SF for all the vehicles & toys, a shop, or the ultimate home gym. Minutes to multiple parks, beaches, Stimpson Nature Reserve, Whole Foods & I-5. Make some minor updates to enhance your lifestyle & build equity at 4725 Austin Ct.

2.82 pastoral and view acreage on Lummi Island with panoramic southwest views of other San Juan Islands and Rosario Strait from every inch of this fantastic property: big sky vistas, captivating southwest light, and beautiful grassy plains. There are very few of these buildable acreages left in this area. Excellent center island location, which allows you to walk to farm stands, post office, beaches, library, restaurant, and school! The property has corners marked, a driveway easement is in place from the private road for development, a shared well is available, and a septic drain field is in place.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School, Ferndale School District

text: Live near Lake Samish in this beautifully updated home in popular Calmor Cove. Part manufactured home, part stick-built, this home features a large, modern kitchen with plenty of counterspace, new cabinets and stainless steel appliances, and a garden window. A versatile floor plan offers plenty of living space indoors. The abundant outdoor living spaces offer private and peaceful views to enjoy nature, complementing the active lakeside lifestyle. Live where there is easy access to Lake Samish with a dock to moor your boat or lake frontage to drop in your kayak, and in a community that enjoys resort style activities all summer! Close to I-5. Potential for Seller financing!

This condo looks over a riparian filled with nature and an abundance of deciduous trees and has a slight view of Mount Baker from the living room and the covered deck. There are no stairs to get to this end unit that has new carpets, sheetrock and paint, due to a frozen sprinkler system in January. Located in walking distance to the Bellis Fair Mall and all the shopping around that area, just a few steps away. This has one covered parking space in the common garage as well as a cage-type storage area. There is crown molding in the living areas and the two bedrooms and baths have great separation. There is a community room and a fitness room, and the HOA dues cover the natural gas for the fireplace insert.
Great little cozy home, large lot, detached garage and storage shed. Room for everyone. Home is sold As Is.

Sweat equity opportunity in this spacious, well-built home ready for your updates! With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths on the main level, a light-filled living room with a gas fireplace, a large dining area, and a bonus room in the basement with a half bath already plumbed for a shower, this home has more to offer than meets the eye. The large lot features a fully fenced and private backyard with a covered deck, patio, garden boxes, fruit trees, and a garden shed. Ample parking is available in the front, and the nicely landscaped and split rail fenced front yard adds to the appeal of the property. A little updating will go a long way in this home. The home is priced with needed updates in mind and in as-is condition.

Live in one of Bellingham's most desirable 55+ communities! This 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom well maintained home is nestled in a beautiful neighborhood and has many recent updates including ductless units, two decks, flooring, paint, appliances, and much more. Both the home and deck have been professionally releveled as well! The cozy yard is fully fenced and has a small art/craft studio. Situated across from Lake Padden, it's close to walking trails, biking trails, golf and swimming. Come and enjoy everything this fabulous community in Bellingham has to offer.

Sought after single-story floor plan overlooking a nature preserve at The Greens @ Loomis Trail! Meticulously maintained home offers effortless living with its convenient layout & upscale design. Great light throughout the oversized windows & vaulted ceilings. Three bedrooms with a private den, 2 baths, a formal dining room this residence is designed for comfort and function. Only 3 steps at the entry and that's it! Practical slate entry--hardwood floors--stainless appliances--granite counters with breakfast bar and eat-in kitchen. Paw-fect for your four legged friends--fully fenced yard, plus garden shed for additional storage. Covered patio is ideal for alfresco dining or simply relaxing and enjoying the beauty of this special place.

Well-kept light and bright home with hardwood floors throughout the main living space, vaulted living room ceiling, skylights, and detached garage. Open kitchen with quartz countertop, tile backsplash, and pantry leads to dining room with charming barn door to separate the living and dining rooms. Primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and attached bath with soaking tub. An additional bedroom, bonus room with a closet, family room, and utility room complete the home. Fully fenced yard includes garden space with raised beds, mature plants, and space for a fire pit. New roof and composite deck added in the last two years. Community features include boat launch, community pool, clubhouse, athletic court, park, playground, and trails.

Point Roberts cozy get away cottage. Walk to everything!! Perfect location for access to Point Roberts amenities. Walk to the Grocery Store, Bank, Post Office, Community Center, Library, Restaurants, Marina and the Beach. Enjoy the cozy living room with wood burning fireplace. Huge fenced yard with new dog run! See it today!

Welcome to this charming craftsman home in the heart of Blaine! This 3 bed, 2 bath gem offers 1, 545 sq ft of well-designed living space, all on one level. Located on a peaceful dead-end street, this newer construction home boasts a prime in-town location. Step inside to discover an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, a stylish kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and modern finishes. A built-in command center desk adds a touch of practicality. The spacious primary suite features a cozy sitting area and a luxurious bathroom. Enjoy year-round comfort with mini splits (A/C) + 2 car garage. Dont miss the opportunity to make this adorable craftsman home yours its the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience!

Enjoy the Comfort and Convenience of Southside Living in this Private Ground-floor Condo nestled among a Serene Forest backdrop. This Inviting Home features 2 Spacious Bedrooms, 2 Baths and an Office/Den space. The Primary Bedroom features a spacious Ensuite and double closets. The Living Area features a Cozy Fireplace and opens to a Partially Enclosed Kitchen, Ideal for Entertaining. Step outside onto the Patio, Perfect for Relaxing and watching the wildlife. Beautifully Maintained Gardens and an Attached Double Garage Enhance the Appeal. The Interurban Trail is nearby leading you to Fairhaven for Shopping, Dining, Parks and the Waterfront. Dont miss out on this low maintenance living in the ideal setting.....Welcome Home!

Enjoy a luxurious life in this beautiful New Custom Built Home. Secluded around green zone in peaceful Sudden Valley this 2900+ sq ft home has no step entry, large windows pouring in natural light among the forest views. From soaring high ceilings to custom built shelves in all 3 walk in closet bedrooms, it has it all! The modern finishes include gorgeous white oak cabinets, quartz countertops, complete stainless steel appliances package and LVP flooring. Main floor master ensuite has a grand soaking tub with an evergreen view and amazing tall glass shower decorated with floor to ceiling tile. Benefit working from home with a main floor office/den room and extra large rec room downstairs w/ a wet bar.

Well cared-for home in Birch Bay Village, 24/7 security with golf course, pool, pickleball, tennis courts and a private marina, see BBV website. Energy efficiency provided by new ductless HP, new instant hot water heater, hot water tank, & new windows throughout. Living room features a cozy wood-burning fireplace & dining room includes built-ins, nice family room adjacent to kitchen is equipped w/ free-standing propane fireplace. Both the primary bedrm & second bedrm come complete with ensuite bthrms. Step outside to a spacious covered front deck, freshly painted exterior & new gutters! Metal roof on home, shed, golf cart garage. Sunny, corner lot, located on a quiet cul-de-sac, is graced with fruit trees & beautiful landscaping.

Welcome to the finest condo living in the heart of Cordata! This exceptional 55+ ground-level home in the gated El Dorado community lives like a house without the hassle of exterior maintenance. Offering 3 spacious bedrooms &2.5 baths across 2, 133 sq. ft., you'll revel in luxurious features including radiant floor heating, a spacious kitchen with granite countertops, built in desk and a primary suite with double doors, and fireplace. Enjoy the convenience of 2 single-car garages, two patios, a formal dining room, and amenities like a clubhouse, greenhouse, dog run, and two furnished rentable condos for visitors. Secure, pet-friendly, and close to shopping, trails, and parksthis is the lifestyle you deserve.

Come home to Salish Breeze and enjoy a peaceful & serene neighborhood. This pristine home is impressive with meticulous attention to every detail. Soaring living room ceilings, kitchen designed for a chef, and endless entertaining, at the end-of-day retreat to your enormous primary suite on main floor, laundry room is a gem. Two beds up, plus a bonus room that boasts a peak of the bay. New high end carpeting throughout. Soak in your hot tub in private backyard with play set, fruit trees and a spotless workshop w/electricity. Unparalleled condition, walking distance to beautiful Birch Bay State Park in a welcoming neighborhood. Detailed list of updates and extras available from your agent. Don't miss this cream puff.

This beautiful country farmhouse sits on 4.5 acres w/ multiple outbuildings and pasture! Boasting over 3200 sqft and 4+ bedrooms make this an ideal space to gather & host. Updated primary suite on main floor. Upstairs is 3 beds & a bonus room, which could potentially be a second primary suite! Lots of improvements were made w/ replacing the roof, septic tank, updated plumbing, crawl space insulation & pump, & water heater (plus so much more). Dreaming of a hobby farm? The barn/shop has so much storage space for your tools & equipment, & parking! Mix in some sweat equity w/ the existing character & charm the possibilities are endless! Great location close to the Canadian border. This amazing property is ready for its next adventure!

Brand New high quality 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 4-plex in upscale multi-family neighborhood. All units have attached garages, Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, self closing cupboards and draws in both kitchen and bathrooms, mini split heat for both heat and air conditioning, quality vinyl plank flooring throughout, 65 gallon remote controlled water heaters.

A lovely Silver Beach single level home with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms and set on a mature, fully fenced .220 acre corner lot... a haven for wildlife and plants. This home has a large living room, dining area and den with birch wood floors, and partial views of Lake Whatcom and the surrounding foothills, and a large covered porch where you can sit and enjoy the evening sun. This sought after location is a delightfully peaceful neighborhood, so bring your remodel designs and make this your place to call home.

Value and opportunity! Two berdroom single wide on a large 65 x 143 Ft. lot. Amazing rear yard with raised garden beds, mature trees and shrubs and a manicured lawn, all bathed in sunshine all day long. The single wide has a small addition with a wood storve to help heat in the cold months. Walk to all amenities, including the beach, parks, restaurant and community center. Post office and grocery store are just down the street. The home needs TLC and some updating, including deferred maintenance. Comes with a storage shed full of tools to help you get started. Value like this seldom is available and the handy-person will love this!

Enjoy the serenity & beauty of a territorial view overlooking Fishtrap Creek, from your private balcony. This open concept, 2 bed, 2 bath, upper level unit is a gem. Plenty of windows allow an abundance of natural light complimenting recent interior paint, gorgeous carpet & wood flooring. Stainless appliances & generous seating surround the kitchens granite peninsula. Vaulted ceilings, newer hot water tank & a cozy gas fireplace are just a few features of this immaculately maintained, move-in ready home. Primary with ensuite, single car garage w/addl parking under cover. This is a prime walkable location offering close proximity to downtown Lynden & key amenities. Minutes to US/Canadian border for fine dining & entertainment.

Just 2 yrs old, this sun-drenched, energy-efficient, 3 bdrm, 2.5 bath home is like-new & very low maintenance.
